# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyConversations/suzyq2.rpy:14
translate chinese suzyq2_b563ed52:

    # ss "How did you know what you wanted to be when you grew up?"
    ss "你小时候是怎么知道自己长大后想做什么的？"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyConversations/suzyq2.rpy:15
translate chinese suzyq2_358ba923:

    # pc "I don't think that I {i}do{/i} know that."
    pc "我觉得我{i}不{/i}知道。"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyConversations/suzyq2.rpy:16
translate chinese suzyq2_6cb7ce9a:

    # ss "Really?"
    ss "真的吗？"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyConversations/suzyq2.rpy:18
translate chinese suzyq2_59b6569d:

    # pc "I always wanted to be like my dad. I was interested in the same types of scientific studies as him."
    pc "我一直想成为像我爸爸那样的人。我对和他一样的科学研究很感兴趣。"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyConversations/suzyq2.rpy:19
translate chinese suzyq2_224d3bb6:

    # pc "But now I'm not so sure."
    pc "但现在我不太确定了。"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyConversations/suzyq2.rpy:21
translate chinese suzyq2_b456a5f5:

    # ss "But you're almost finished with school. If you don't use that degree, it'll all be a waste."
    ss "可你快毕业了。如果你不用那个学位，那一切就都白费了。"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyConversations/suzyq2.rpy:22
translate chinese suzyq2_5b22d737:

    # pc "Maybe."
    pc "也许吧。"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyConversations/suzyq2.rpy:24
translate chinese suzyq2_80d7f5e0:

    # pc "I think most people just stumble around until they find something they enjoy doing."
    pc "我觉得大多数人都是摸索着走，直到找到自己喜欢做的事。"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyConversations/suzyq2.rpy:25
translate chinese suzyq2_318ff1b2:

    # pc "Or at least something that they can tolerate."
    pc "或者至少是能忍受的事。"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyConversations/suzyq2.rpy:27
translate chinese suzyq2_2498476a:

    # ss "I just don't know what to do."
    ss "我就是不知道该做什么。"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyConversations/suzyq2.rpy:28
translate chinese suzyq2_abc32ec3:

    # ss "It's really scary being out of high school. This is like the first time that my life hasn't been planned out."
    ss "高中毕业后真的很让人害怕。这好像是我人生中第一次没有既定计划。"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyConversations/suzyq2.rpy:29
translate chinese suzyq2_2e4fa4d2:

    # ss "I've always wanted freedom, but now that I can do anything I want, I don't know what to do."
    ss "我一直想要自由，但现在虽然可以随心所欲，却不知道该做什么。"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyConversations/suzyq2.rpy:30
translate chinese suzyq2_b124ff06:

    # ss "I'm almost done with my basics at college now. I have to make a choice."
    ss "我现在大学的基础课程快修完了，必须做出选择。"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyConversations/suzyq2.rpy:31
translate chinese suzyq2_0fbd043b:

    # pc "Have you talked to a counselor?"
    pc "你找过辅导员聊过吗？"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyConversations/suzyq2.rpy:33
translate chinese suzyq2_ed4cce59:

    # ss "Yeah, Mrs. Spann is really nice, but she can't make the decision for me."
    ss "聊过，斯潘恩女士人很好，但她不能替我做决定。"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyConversations/suzyq2.rpy:34
translate chinese suzyq2_a5b6b729:

    # ss "She suggested that I maybe take a year off, go somewhere, try out some new things, find out what I like."
    ss "她建议我或许可以休学一年，去某个地方，尝试些新事物，找出自己喜欢什么。"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyConversations/suzyq2.rpy:35
translate chinese suzyq2_4aa50788:

    # pc "That's not a bad idea. Gertrude is pretty smart."
    pc "这主意不错。格特鲁德挺聪明的。"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyConversations/suzyq2.rpy:37
translate chinese suzyq2_8ce17b10:

    # ss "Gertrude? You're on a first name basis with her?"
    ss "格特鲁德？你跟她都直呼其名了？"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyConversations/suzyq2.rpy:38
translate chinese suzyq2_cfabca70:

    # pc "I guess so?"
    pc "大概吧？"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyConversations/suzyq2.rpy:40
translate chinese suzyq2_e704463b:

    # ss "Whatever. Anyway, maybe I'll do that."
    ss "管他呢。总之，我可能就这么干。"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyConversations/suzyq2.rpy:41
translate chinese suzyq2_7e81f166:

    # ss "Travel. Try some different jobs."
    ss "去旅行。尝试不同的工作。"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyConversations/suzyq2.rpy:42
translate chinese suzyq2_13348ec8:

    # ss "Find myself."
    ss "找到真正的自己。"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyConversations/suzyq2.rpy:43
translate chinese suzyq2_100e411a:

    # pc "That sounds like it might be fun."
    pc "听起来挺有意思的。"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyConversations/suzyq2.rpy:45
translate chinese suzyq2_088247e2:

    # ss "Want to come with me?"
    ss "要不要跟我一起去？"

# game/Scenes/Suzy/SuzyConversations/suzyq2.rpy:46
translate chinese suzyq2_7034f885:

    # pc "Maybe I will."
    pc "说不定我会去。"

